                        <p style="margin: 0;padding: 0;font-size: 16px;font-family: 'Avenir Next', &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Helvetica&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;line-height: 1.65;font-weight: normal;margin-bottom: 20px;">The <a href="https://lists.gbif.org/mailman/listinfo/api-users">GBIF API users list</a> provides an active peer-to-peer discussion
